schools.name: Palm Bay Magnet Senior High School

data.description: Set back on over a third of an acre lies this charming brick home that has been remodeled and is ready for new owners. Plenty of yard on this one with a large fenced in dog run plus a lot of extra space and a big shed makes it a great place for entertaining. Conveniently located very close to Hammock Landing, Publix, and I-95 makes it an ideal location. A wide open floorplan really brings the scope of the space into focus and provides a warm and welcoming feeling of home.
